divs: Sighting DetailsDiamond like orb hovering in the sky about 1 mile to 2 miles away, from where I was it looked to be about the size of a skittle or m&m. It stayed in about the same place for 45 mins and then lowered quite quickly below a neighboring treeline, but then slowly hovered back up at a 90 degree angle back to about the same place i had first seen it. its been about 2 hrs now, and still visible. but here and there moves slightly up and down. Hope since this thing is just "hangin" around like this in such a populated area, that someone else will see and or report it as well.
